features: 💡Eye-protecting & Organizer: With professional round design and lamp beads, this desk lamp for dorm can shine a flicker-free and no dizzy light. No shadow and No unnecessary flash. Suitable for reading, writing, drawing, and crafting. The LED desk lights for home office feature pen holders and a phone mount that can help keep your desk tidy and give you lots of conveniences.

💡Remotrol Control & Timing-There are color temperature, brightness adjustment, timing, night light, and switch buttons on the remote control. Accurate remote control within 1 m. The small desk lamp has 3 timing settings, 15 mins, 30 mins and 60 mins timing, let the study lamp turn off auto at a fixed time to save electricity. Especially suitable for use before going to bed. A great reading lamps for bedside table.

💡3 Lighting Modes & Infinite Brightness- With a sensitive touch switch or remote control, you can freely switch 3 lighting modes-white light, warm light and warm white light. In each mode, the brightness of this kids desk lamp can be adjusted to suit your various lighting needs. The lamp feature a physical switch, you can turn off the lamp directly without having to repeatedly press the touch switch to turn off the light like other led desk lamp.

💡Flexible and Space-saver- Flexible Hose of this study lamp can be bent at any angle, allowing you to adjust it with ease and to direct the light wherever you want. It is small and lightweight, foldable and portable. Without a cord, this cordless desk lamp can fit in your small spaces, suitable for kids/women/men's crowded desks. Also a perfect desk lamp for college dorm room and desk lamps for home office.

💡4000 mAh & Stabler- Built-in 4000 mAh large capacity Li-ion battery, making the led lights for desk be just charged for 4 hours but can work up to 4 to 40 hours. The Type-c charging port makes charging faster and safer. The base of the table lamp has four silicone pads, which can stand on the desk more stably, without worrying about adjusting the angle of the lamp for desk and causing it to fall over. (Note: Don't include charger/adapter)

manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: FgineCoo’s latest upgraded table lamp FgineCoo’s latest upgraded table lamp is available in two colors: white and pink. The latest upgrade is from a ring lampshade to a round lampshade, and the base has also been reinforced. The entire table lamp has been upgraded with materials and workmanship to avoid the problem of shell cracking. Give you a better experience and a better desk lamp.

The light is soft and not dazzling The lamp head of this table lamp adopts a multi-stage filter, with a total of 24 lamp beads. The soft light plate prevents the light from being too bright and dazzling, making the eyes more comfortable. The table lamp is equipped with an anti-blue light board, which can more effectively reduce blue light, and can effectively relieve eye fatigue, dry eyes and other problems. It also has certain benefits for preventing myopia in children. Better protect children's eyes. At the same time, the table lamp is also equipped with a heat sink, so you may worry that turning on the light for a long time will cause the table lamp to overheat.

3 color temperature level and stepless dimming It has 3 color temperatures and stepless dimming function, which you can adjust to meet different needs in different environments. Better protect your eyes.

Built-in high-capacity battery This desk lamp has a built-in 4000 mAh battery, which can last for 5-24 hours depending on the frequency of use and brightness. The large-capacity battery makes this desk lamp not only provide daily lighting, but also can be used as a home emergency light.

Charging is more convenient The table lamp is equipped with a USB-C cable, which can be charged with an adapter, or it can be charged with a power bank or a power strip with a USB port. NOTE: The desk lamp does not come with an adapter. ON-OFF button When you want to turn off the lamp, you can directly use this button to turn off it quickly. There is an indicator light next to the charging port, which is red when charging and green when fully charged. Phone Holder/Pen Holder The multifunctional storage rack is both a pen holder and a mobile phone holder, keeping your desktop clean. Eye protection desk lamp The light is uniform and soft, with three modes of white light, yellow light, and yellow-white light, which can better protect the eyes and is the best choice for night work, study, and reading.

The desk lamp has uniform light, no glare and no flicker, more eye-friendly, and effectively reduces blue light damage. It is a very good eye-protecting led desk lamp. The LED Desk Lamp with Pen Holder is also an absolute must-have for your office workspace, home desk area, or dorm room. The unique design of the LED desk lamp makes it a suitable occasion gift for students, parents, family and friends.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 24, 2023
reviews.reviewText: It is super cute, elegant, helpful, bright and just the perfect siize for a medium desk. My desk has 2 shelves and they both get the light that I need to study, read or just to see something I need at night like a medicine, whatever bottle, my phone charger, etc.I love the look, the texture, the brightness, the size, its just perfect, and the fact that I can set it to turn of is amazing as well!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 4, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Awesome and great value!
reviews.reviewText: I needed a lamp for my desk I could use to both light my keyboard at night AND to light me while I did webinars. This works great as I can aim the gooseneck up so it shines on me or down to they keyboard.I love the multiple settings and the remote. It even has a timer function to turn it off… not sure why you’d need that.It has three light styles… bright white, warm white and an amber with a dimmer for all.It can be charged and used without a cord at all or left plugged into a USB port.The base could be a bit heavier but I just put some change in it to weight it. Then I store the remote in the cup.
